
<h1>The Power of Crosswalk</h1>

<h2>Reduced Fragmentation</h2>
<p>The immediate benefit of bundling an application with the Crosswalk webview is that everywhere your application runs, it uses the same, Chromium-based runtime. This reduces or eliminates many of the headaches encountered with older webviews.  <small>(The web app run below uses Web Components and WebGL.)</small></p>

