<h2>SIMD: Parallel Execution</h2>

<p>An advanced feature available on x86-based devices is <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/SIMD">SIMD</a>: the ability to leverage the CPU to run data calculations in parallel. SIMD.js is a Javascript library that gives this ability to web apps.</p>

